    <h1>Privacy Policy for Dinosaur Prehistoric Hunter VR</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last updated: June 10, 2025</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>When you play Dinosaur Prehistoric Hunter VR on Meta Horizon, we collect:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Meta Account ID</strong> - Used to enable game features and multiplayer functionality</li>
        <li><strong>Device Information</strong> - Hardware model, operating system version, and VR headset type</li>
        <li><strong>Gameplay Data</strong> - Session duration, achievements, in-game actions, and progression</li>
        <li><strong>Performance Data</strong> - Crash reports and performance metrics to improve stability</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do <strong>not</strong> collect: Your real name, email address, physical location, or payment information.</p>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>To provide and maintain game functionality</li>
        <li>To improve gameplay experience and fix technical issues</li>
        <li>To analyze player behavior for game optimization</li>
        <li>To deliver software updates and new content</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We share information with:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Meta Platforms, Inc.</strong> - Required for Horizon platform services and features</li>
        <li><strong>Unity Technologies</strong> - For analytics and crash reporting (<a href="https://unity.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank">view Unity's policy</a>)</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>We do not sell your personal data</strong> to advertisers or third parties.</p>

    <h2>4. Your Privacy Rights</h2>
    <p>You can:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Request deletion of your data by emailing us at <a href="mailto:abdurrehman.mma12327@gmail.com">abdurrehman.mma12327@gmail.com</a></li>
        <li>Manage privacy settings through your <a href="https://accounts.meta.com/settings" target="_blank">Meta account</a></li>
        <li>Opt-out of analytics through your device settings</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We will respond to all requests within 30 days.</p>

    <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
    <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your information. However, no method of electronic transmission is 100% secure.</p>

    <h2>6. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>Our game is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from users under 13.</p>

    <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy. The "Last updated" date at the top will reflect changes. Continued use of the game means you accept the updated policy.</p>

    <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>For privacy questions or requests:</p>
    <p>Email: <a href="mailto:abdurrehman.mma12327@gmail.com">abdurrehman.mma12327@gmail.com</a></p>
